{"hdbbe6758g0e0bg40b5g9912g2c6b9419360b": ["My beautiful, penitent child. ", "cad1854b-8f41-4038-b640-156ee0272f81", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_PainPriest_PostPenance.html", "87440f1c-eb4c-8670-08ec-ebe6d597b4ea"], "h9736ff0dg0fbbg453ag9af6g683467fa5d5e": ["You have already enjoyed my ministrations - do not be greedy. ", "cad1854b-8f41-4038-b640-156ee0272f81", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_PainPriest_PostPenance.html", "d451fd94-13be-4cb2-7fa3-c31e4a0eb9c1"], "hbf466293gfc50g454fgbb88g1021a61e072d": ["Loviatar herself found your performance<i> inspiring </i>and wishes to bless you. ", "cad1854b-8f41-4038-b640-156ee0272f81", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_PainPriest_PostPenance.html", "346c7f07-80a0-5109-35d8-af2494be424d"], "hc469446dg3593g419bg93f8g89444d00680f": ["What would such a blessing entail?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_PainPriest_PostPenance.html", "8e8a56ef-bc42-1644-6f10-0041cbdb7b31"], "he9fbb2a7g0753g476eg8214g6f8273fd2054": ["Simply be still, dear one. ", "cad1854b-8f41-4038-b640-156ee0272f81", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_PainPriest_PostPenance.html", "6194cb1f-e8e7-7304-cffd-0f691237f77e"], "ha80c2380g8fecg470bg99d2gde666daa5547": ["And on a personal note, thank you. That was positively <i>divine. </i>", "cad1854b-8f41-4038-b640-156ee0272f81", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_PainPriest_PostPenance.html", "33348e45-96ad-2ef9-9124-66de616e9d0e"], "h1f405486g0a27g438bgb31bg5c4f9cab87ee": ["<i>Leave. </i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_PainPriest_PostPenance.html", "da1347e3-460e-224a-c63d-848bb9733dc2"], "hca5f6497gea01g48d4ga7c1gd49473800572": ["A most <i>invigorating </i>session - but even as the soul sings, the flesh fades. ", "cad1854b-8f41-4038-b640-156ee0272f81", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_PainPriest_PostPenance.html", "59017772-53c8-d8fb-3f42-8878e3375c01"], "h28343503gdedcg46b6ga7afg6931675b63cd": ["So it is with the Lady's embrace. Excuse me - I must rest and think.", "cad1854b-8f41-4038-b640-156ee0272f81", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_PainPriest_PostPenance.html", "f26c6b65-cc82-f211-493c-b5cd9d118614"], "h92155023g80a1g4303gb3d5g9d405652b3bb": ["Excuse me - I must rest and think.", "cad1854b-8f41-4038-b640-156ee0272f81", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_PainPriest_PostPenance.html", "4f5da17d-846a-896a-d913-663564ba6fa5"]}